snippet.title: TYPECAST Announcement Trailer
snippet.description:
TYPECAST is a bullet hell shooter where you type to shoot. Get swarmed by enemies, manage the chaos, and climb the leaderboards in this unique arcade experience.

Presented by Gutter Arcade, a subsidiary of Official Electric. 

No one was harmed in the making of this trailer.
